java.lang.Object
com.conquest.duelHandler.DuelSessionModel
public class DuelSessionModel extends Object
ðŸ§© DuelSessionModel Represents a multi-player duel session between two teams. Tracks player states, teleportation, eliminations, disconnections, and outcome.
